      <p class="text-xs font-semibold text-zinc-700 mt-6 mx-auto text-center">By continuing, you agree to Pinterest's Terms of Service and acknowledge you've read our Privacy Policy. Notice at collection.</p>
      <a class="inline-block mt-4 text-sm text-center w-full font-semibold text-zinc-600" href="/register">Not on Pinterest yet? Sign up</a>
